wcase games for USABasketball, as themen's national team will play South Sudan and Germanyat O2 Arena on July 20 and July 22, respectively.\", \"from\": 255, \"to\": 428, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 382, \"end\": 390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_O2_Arena\", \"score\": 0.9999365508081615, \"rank\": 6.344498903313051e-05, \"text\": \"O2 Arena\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_O2_Arena\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_O2_Arena\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement  \\\"USA Basketball is looking forward to adding our women's national team to the USA Basketball Showcase in London,\\\" Jim Tooley, the CEO of USA Basketball said in a news release.\", \"from\": 430, \"to\": 620, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 523, \"end\": 537, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Basketball\", \"score\": 0.9999999999795364, \"rank\": 2.0575363445971012e-11, \"text\": \"USA Basketball\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Basketball\"}, {\"begin\": 538, \"end\": 546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Showcase\", \"score\": 0.9999622507684073, \"rank\": 3.543267886438523e-05, \"text\": \"Showcase\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Showcase\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Showcase\"}, {\"begin\": 550, \"end\": 556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999790920836168, \"rank\": 2.0819338350530226e-05, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 582, \"end\": 596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Basketball\", \"score\": 0.9999999999795364, \"rank\": 2.0575363445971012e-11, \"text\": \"USA Basketball\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wik