ails and final team rosters, will be announced at a later date.\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1671, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1529, \"end\": 1543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Basketball\", \"score\": 0.9999999999795364, \"rank\": 2.0575363445971012e-11, \"text\": \"USA Basketball\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Basketball\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The U.S. women's national team will be looking to win an eighth consecutive gold medal in the upcomingOlympics.\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1784, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Who will be on Team USA and try to do so remains in question as theWNBAseason approaches.\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1875, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1801, \"end\": 1809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9919611482560605, \"rank\": 0.004838805496930404, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"USA Basketball held recent pre-Olympic training camps in early February and in Cleveland during the women's Final Four.\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1995, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1876, \"end\": 1890, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Basketball\", \"score\": 0.9999999999795364, \"rank\": 2.0575363445971012e-11, \"text\": \"USA Basketball\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Basketball\"}, {\"begin\": 1955, \"end\": 1964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cleveland_Cavaliers\", \"score\": 0.9999248821875468, \"rank\": 7.385298324973773e-05, \"text\": \"Cleveland\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cleveland_Cavaliers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cleveland_Cavaliers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The final team could ultimately make a statement about what the committee values: youth and the future or experience and proven success.Caitlin Clark, the presumptive No.\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2166, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"1 pick in Monday's WNBA Draft, is in the selection pool, though she has yet to attend a senior national team camp this cycle.\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2292, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2186, \"end\": 2190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.84054622777127e-14, \"text\": \"WNBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_National_Basketball_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was invited to the camp in Cleveland but did not participate after Iowa advanced to the Final Four.\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2396, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2324, \"end\": 2333, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cleveland_Cavaliers\", \"score\": 0.9999248821875468, \"rank\": 7.385298324973773e-05, \"text\": \"Cleveland\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cleveland_Cavaliers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cleveland_Cavaliers\"}, {\"begin\": 2364, \"end\": 2368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iowa_Hawkeyes_football\", \"score\": 0.7640992533159718, \"rank\": 0.25282176228672426, \"text\": \"Iowa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iowa_Hawkeyes_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iowa_Hawkeyes_football\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement  Other potential first-time Olympic participants invited to recent camps includeAliyah Boston,Rhyne Howard,Sabrina Ionescu,Arike OgunbowaleandShakira Austin.Allisha GrayandJackie Youngboth won gold medals in 3\\u00d73 at the Tokyo Games but would be first-time 5-on-5 Olympic participants.Diana Taurasiis poised to be the group's veteran, as she's looking to win a sixth consecutive gold.\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2794, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When we invite people to be part of USA Basketball training camp, sometimes it's with an eye to the future,\\\" women's national team committee chair Jennifer Rizzotti said during the February camp.\", \"from\": 2796, \"to\": 2992, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2833, \"end\": 2847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Basketball\", \"score\": 0.9999999999795364, \"rank\": 2.0575363445971012e-11, \"text\": \"USA Basketball\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Basketball\"}, {\"begin\": 2944, \"end\": 2961, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jennifer_Rizzotti\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jennifer Rizzotti\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jennifer_Rizzotti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jennifer_Rizzotti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can remember when Aliyah Boston was at her first mini-camp, I can remember whenBreanna Stewartwas at her first national team camp, I can remember when many players have come to camp when they were in college or maybe just finishing college, and some made Olympic teams and some of them did not.\", \"from\": 2993, \"to\": 3290, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3014, \"end\": 3027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aliyah_Boston\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aliyah Boston\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aliyah_Boston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aliyah_Boston\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think it's about giving them that exposure.\\\"\", \"from\": 3291, \"to\": 3337, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stewart played with the senior national team at the 2014 World Cup and in the 2015 Pan American Games in Toronto before making her Olympic debut at the 2016 Rio Games, months removed from the end of her college career at UConn.\", \"from\": 3339, \"to\": 3566, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3339, \"end\": 3346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breanna_Stewart\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.084876083937294e-30, \"text\": \"Stewart\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breanna_Stewart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breanna_Stewart\"}, {\"begin\": 3422, \"end\": 3440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pan_American_Games\", \"score\": 0.999888803749871, \"rank\": 0.00010441009559505893, \"text\": \"Pan American Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pan_American_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pan_American_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 3444, \"end\": 3451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto_Raptors\", \"score\": 0.9954645674906866, \"rank\": 0.0038402831371547536, \"text\": \"Toronto\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto_Raptors\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto_Raptors\"}, {\"begin\": 3560, \"end\": 3565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UConn_Huskies_women's_basketball\", \"score\": 0.9999999999818101, \"rank\": 1.8227041796671153e-11, \"text\": \"UConn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UConn_Huskies_women's_basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UConn_Huskies_women's_basketball\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Taurasi was the youngest player on the 2004 gold-medal-winning team in Athens.\", \"from\": 3567, \"to\": 3645, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3638, \"end\": 3644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999999999965894, \"rank\": 3.431845146342511e-11, \"text\": \"Athens\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"USA Basketball has always been a certain way of play, where you put everything that you do well aside for the betterment of the team,\\\" Taurasi said last week.\", \"from\": 3647, \"to\": 3806, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It does not matter who wears the jersey, the style of play is the same.\", \"from\": 3807, \"to\": 3879, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You try to share the ball, you try to play together and try to play unselfish and the ultimate goal is to win no matter who has the jersey on.\\\"\", \"from\": 3880, \"to\": 4023, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(Photo: Mike Lawrie / Getty Images)  Spot the pattern.\", \"from\": 4025, \"to\": 4079, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4047, \"end\": 4052, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.9999850765156566, \"rank\": 1.3567378714639026e-05, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Connect the terms  Find the hidden link between sports terms  Play today's puzzle\", \"from\": 4080, \"to\": 4161, \"entities\": []}]}"